	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Here's an <a href="http://fontstruct.com/fontstructions/show/919913" class="postlink">8x8 monospaced font</a> I call SDS 8x8! The SDS stands for Super Dragonsin Saga, which is the project I originally made this for.<br /><br />It's a multi-purpose font I made years ago and I've slowly honed it to perfection over the years as I've used it for my projects. If you want to add this font to a CHR page, I suggest you download it and manually type it into a 128x128 image. This method works well and allows for a lot of flexibility as far as the arrangement of tiles.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


